media:group.media:title: Streaming Live: The Vox Channel
media:group.media:description:
Thoughtfully curated, thoroughly explained. 

You’re watching a special livestream: our linear TV channel that brings together the best of Vox and other networks at our parent company Vox Media, including @The Verge, @Eater, @Secret Base, and more.

This week we’re bringing the stream to YouTube so you can discover our favorite work across Vox Media, from policy and politics to food and pop culture, and everything in between. 

If you see something you like, make sure to hit subscribe so you never miss a new Vox video. http://goo.gl/0bsAjO And if you’re loving this TV format, after this week you can catch The Vox Channel on Roku channel 579!

For more info on our Vox Media networks, check out their individual YouTube channels:
The Verge: https://www.youtube.com/c/TheVerge 
Eater: https://www.youtube.com/c/eater 
Secret Base: https://www.youtube.com/c/SecretBaseSBN
